Class RunInfo

java.lang.Object
  fi.hu.cs.titokone.DebugInfo
      fi.hu.cs.titokone.RunInfo
public class RunInfo
extends DebugInfo

This class tells GUIBrain what the processor has done. RunDebugger creates objects from this class and passes them to onwards.
